n be sensitive to short‑term factors; monitoring leading indicators (traffic, promotions) will help anticipate future swings.  \n\nA simple line plot of the provided data will instantly convey this story, making it easy for stakeholders to see both the **overall growth** and the **month‑to‑month volatility**.'}}, 'id': 'call_abe275b01224', 'type': 'tool_call'}, {'name': 'generate_visualization_tool', 'args': {'tool_input': {'query': 'Plot monthly transaction count from inception to date', 'data': [{'month': '2022-01-01T00:00:00+00:00', 'transaction_count': 124}, {'month': '2022-02-01T00:00:00+00:00', 'transaction_count': 98}, {'month': '2022-03-01T00:00:00+00:00', 'transaction_count': 110}, {'month': '2022-04-01T00:00:00+00:00', 'transaction_count': 87}, {'month': '2022-05-01T00:00:00+00:00', 'transaction_count': 132}], 'state': {}}}, 'id': 'call_120f19350b25', 'type': 'tool_call'}, {'name': 'generate_visualization_tool', 'args': {'query': 'Plot monthly transaction count from inception to date', 'data': [{'month': '2022-01-01T00:00:00+00:00', 'transaction_count': 124}, {'month': '2022-02-01T00:00:00+00:00', 'transaction_count': 98}, {'month': '2022-03-01T00:00:00+00:00', 'transaction_count': 110}, {'month': '2022-04-01T00:00:00+00:00', 'transaction_count': 87}, {'month': '2022-05-01T00:00:00+00:00', 'transaction_count': 132}], 'state': {}}, 'id': 'call_67d6ce9e853e', 'type': 'tool_call'}], invalid_tool_calls=[]), ToolMessage(content="Error executing tool: 1 validation error for sql_query_tool\nquery\n  Field required [type=missing, input_value={'tool_input': {'query': ...month volatility**.'}}, input_type=dict]\n    For further information visit https://errors.pydantic.dev/2.12/v/missing", name='error_handler', id='92db4589-b493-4933-8998-e9ab3d78bf49', tool_call_id='error'), AIMessage(content='', additional_kwargs={}, response_metadata={}, id='lc_run--019cd74c-e0ad-7c52-9f75-4d1e554c3d58-0', tool_calls=[{'name': 'generate_visualization_tool', 'args': {'query': 'Plo